  <div class="section_services">
    <div class="section_services-wrapper">
      <div class="section_services-container">
        <div class="section_services-title-wrapper">
          <div class="section_services-title-container">
            <h1 class="section-title font-athelas-bold"><span class="section-blue-font">(More)</span> services</h1>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section_services-tabs">
          <button class="section_services-tablink open-tab" onclick="showTab(this, 'websites')" target="websites" id="defaultTab"><p class="section_services-tablink-title font-metropolis-regular">Websites</p></button>
          <button class="section_services-tablink" onclick="showTab(this, 'eCommerce')" target="eCommerce"><p class="section_services-tablink-title font-metropolis-regular">E-commerce</p></button>
          <button class="section_services-tablink" onclick="showTab(this, 'software')" target="software"><p class="section_services-tablink-title font-metropolis-regular">Software Development</p></button>
        </div>
        <div class="section_services-tabs-wrapper">
          <div id="websites" class="section_services-tabcontent-wrapper">
          <img class="section_services-tabcontent-img hide-on-mobile" src="img/services-websites.jpg" alt="Image to services">
            <img class="section_services-tabcontent-img show-on-mobile" src="img/services-websites-m.jpg" alt="Image to services">
            <div class="section_services-tabcontent">
              <p class="section_services-tabcontent-title font-metropolis-bold">Make a great first impression</p>
              <div class="section_services-tabcontent-divider hide-on-mobile"></div>
              <p class="section_services-tabcontent-text font-athelas-regular hide-on-mobile">Your Website is your new business card. Why don’t make it amazing? With less text and more images make your customers fall in love with your service or product, understand it and have a great user experience. Show them now you’re the right choice.</p>
              <a href="services.html">
                <div class="section_services-btn">
                  <p class="font-metropolis-medium">Services</p>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id ="eCommerce" class="section_services-tabcontent-wrapper" style="display:none;">
          <img class="section_services-tabcontent-img hide-on-mobile" src="img/services-eCommerce.jpg" alt="Image to services">
            <img class="section_services-tabcontent-img show-on-mobile" src="img/services-eCommerce-m.jpg" alt="Image to services">
            <div class="section_services-tabcontent">
              <p class="section_services-tabcontent-title font-metropolis-bold">Sell your service or product</p>
              <div class="section_services-tabcontent-divider hide-on-mobile"></div>
              <p class="section_services-tabcontent-text font-athelas-regular hide-on-mobile">Wether you’re a big or small company, you create or manufacture your products, or even if you sell a service, we can help you to become a real online business by designing and developing a beautiful store for you. You will reach millions of customers by creating an amazing buying experience.</p>
              <img src="img/logos/shopify-white.png" alt="Shopify logo">
              <a href="services.html">
                <div class="section_services-btn">
                  <p class="font-metropolis-medium">Services</p>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="software" class="section_services-tabcontent-wrapper" style="display:none;">
          <img class="section_services-tabcontent-img hide-on-mobile" src="img/services-software.jpg" alt="Image to services">
            <img class="section_services-tabcontent-img show-on-mobile" src="img/services-software-m.jpg" alt="Image to services">
            <div class="section_services-tabcontent">
              <p class="section_services-tabcontent-title font-metropolis-bold">Tailor made Software</p>
              <div class="section_services-tabcontent-divider hide-on-mobile"></div>
              <p class="section_services-tabcontent-text font-athelas-regular hide-on-mobile">Anything you can imagine is real. Technology is the best way for creating new companies, products and any software you have in mind. We want to hear all your challenges so we can use technology to overcome them. Create something amazing with us!</p>
              <a href="services.html">
                <div class="section_services-btn">
                  <p class="font-metropolis-medium">Services</p>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
